# Hunting Business OSINT

- Google and visit company website
- Can start with LinkedIn
    - number, website, where
    - can try to see badge, dress code, employees
    - By searching their title/description in quotes, you can get a direct link to an otherwise private profile
        - good trick here is Google search: site:linkedin.com “* at <company name>/in”
- Try other social media
- Open Corporates - https://opencorporates.com/
    - type in company name
    - seems just okay
- AI HIT - https://www.aihitdata.com/
    - similar, but may glean new info
- Indeed
    - Job postings tell some technologies and languages
